Package api.equinix.javasdk.customerportal.enums

package api.equinix.javasdk.customerportal.enums
Customer Portal enumerations for the Equinix Java SDK. Defines typed constants for order types (OrderType), order statuses (OrderStatus), ticket priorities (TicketPriority), ticket statuses (TicketStatus), shipment statuses (ShipmentStatus), cross-connect types, smart hands types, work visit statuses, case priorities, asset types, and other Customer Portal domain values.
